This LICENSE file contains the short license notice. The full canonical
text of the GNU General Public License v3.0 MUST be placed alongside it
before this project is distributed.

Canonical text:  https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt
Plain HTML:      https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.html

To complete the LICENSE in this repository, run:

    curl -fsSL https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt -o COPYING

This places the full canonical license text in a file named COPYING
(the GNU convention). Both LICENSE and COPYING together satisfy GPL-3.0
distribution requirements. GitHub's license detection recognises this
layout and labels the repository correctly as GPL-3.0-or-later.

Until COPYING is in place, this project is not ready for public
distribution.

